{
  "stem": "11797.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He has very, very good ways about himself, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always admired him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he had the right decisions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to help us, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to worry about us, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to worry about him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were very close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '42-- this was happening in '42-- so I was-- '42, I was 17.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was very small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took us into a small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The remaining-- they made-- from the big ghetto who went away to Majdanek or to Treblinka or someplace else, you know, they formed-- a small ghetto is formed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this ghetto was located in Radom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It consisted of about three or four streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put us up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fortunately, my apartment-- or our apartment was very close to a-- to the street-- to the corner-- to the wall where they shot people for any crime.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you talked too much, if you walk-- walk bad and all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you did any kind of crime, you were put to the wall-- [INAUDIBLE] wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You were shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you can imagine, that wall must have-- must have had thousands of bullets, of holes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even it didn't go through the building, because in Europe, they build the buildings with three or four layers of bricks now for the walls.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it didn't go through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when we went outside, you now, we saw-- there was a lot of huge, big holes, you know, in the wall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we stayed there all-- my brother, myself, my father stayed there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's-- that-- oh, golly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like eating the matzo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, like, every minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
